Chordate laughed as he saw Feline blush and giggle.  He kissed her on the 
nose.  

"Well, don't be embarrassed, I never kiss someone I just met a little while 
ago either.  I'm not sure of an exact place to walk.  I haven't exactly been 
here that long.  And--woah, I totally forgot about something.  Heh.  I'm 
going to have to go soon, would you like me to show you your quarters?"
